Text: RE ChevronHPL Compression Agreement Cc June Draftdoc Please take a look at this and let me know what you think Ed Wick Original Message From Eric Gillaspie SMTP Sent Monday June PM To George Weissman Cheryl Lantz Marshall Cc Gerald Nemec Subject ChevronHPL Compression Agreement Mr Wick Attached for your review and comment is the HPLChevron Compression Agreement we recently discussed Your requested changes have been implemented into the document If you have any questions or comments please feel free to reach me at the number below or Gerald Nemec at It was a pleasure working with you See attached file ChevronCompression June Draftdoc Thanks Eric Gillaspie Enron Building File Mac Word ChevronCompression June Draftdoc
